### OpenFlow 1.3.1 HELLO message
## This one announces that it supports 1.0 and 1.2
#
# highest supported openflow version (u8) = 1.2 (0x3)
#<0>#
03

# message type (u8) = OFPT_HELLO(0)
00

# message length (u16) = 16
00 10

# transaction id (u32) = 0
00 00 00 00

### Message Specific Payload - Hello elements
# This one is VERSION_BITMAP, supporting 1.0 and 1.2 Only

# hello element type (u16) = 1 (VERSION_BITMAP)
#<8>#
00 01

# length in bytes of this element (u16) = 8
00 08

# First bitmap (versions 0 to 31)
# V_1_0 : 1 << 0x01  = 0x02
# V_1_2 : 1 << 0x03  = 0x08
#<12>#
00 00 00 0a

## Zero-Filled Padding to bring total structure length to multiple of 8
## element struct length is 8; add 0 to bring it to 8

#<16>#
####### and we are done #######
